{"tid":1005725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冬季流感高峰期講兩句","createTime":"2019-02-02T12:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T12:12:47.000Z","uid":138409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3de454a0a38a764b7be9a0bd787b5dd6c8cb0b56","tid":1005725,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/artstudentinmedicine/posts/386300465482689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fartstudentinmedicine%2Fposts%2F386300465482689&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=d04792ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/artstudentinmedicine/posts/386300465482689</a><br />\n自從黃醫生係100毛個訪問出咗之後就有不少的政界人士或左翼分子認為將醫療系統崩潰的問題歸咎於新移民係歧視，沒有數據支持作出指責，實為有欠醫德云云。<br />\n<br />\n係香港，甚至世界各地，我地唔難發現會有一班鍵盤左膠戰士永遠拿著歧視和大愛的旗幟站在道德高地批判世人，把一些冠冕堂皇，聽起來好動聽很有愛很有人類精神的吶喊說話去叫人要包容、要認識、要理解新移民的苦況等等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但你會發現，呢班左膠永遠都是<br />\n一。樣。事。情。都。無。做。過。<br />\n永遠只係識講同叫人做、叫人包容、叫人盡責</span><br />\n<br />\n症唔係你睇、房唔係你巡、手術唔係你做、藥唔係你開、影像掃描唔係你睇、文件唔係你填、所有嘢都唔係你班左膠做的時候，你當然係口響嫁<br />\n<br />\n你有無落手落腳幫手處理呢個崩壞緊的醫療體系？無！<br />\n<br />\n望住香港長期100-150%病房使用率你做過d咩？無！<br />\n<br />\n見住一班新移民一落黎香港就洗腎全餐時，你做過d咩？叫人唔好歧視再問人攞數據支持新移民會使用香港公立服務？<br />\n<br />\n你係咪從來無去過公立醫院？<span style=\"color: gold;\">無見過愈來愈多講國語M字頭身分證的病人？<br />\n</span><br />\n係公立醫院到做醫護的人如果唔清楚到底新移民點樣佔用香港公立服務，唔通你班乜L嘢都無做過的左膠會比較清楚？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大義凜然地講動聽說話去講要爭取普世價值其實邊個唔識講？個問題係香港崩潰至此，連本地人都未應付到，未提供到基本醫療服務時，仲講乜L嘢要照顧埋新移民？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">已經唔期望你班左膠幫忙，但至少可唔可以唔好係醫護水深火熱之時雪中送屎？<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c1e32749e36b378a4c40bfdcf6937ec7e79041b7","tid":1005725,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"33e3db7eab7d2cd1cb60e07f5fe9aae9bc56e70c","tid":1005725,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:06:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"383baa3de01cab8b8534b17e5827d6603819723f","tid":1005725,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈要求引入中國醫生</span> </span></strong><br />\n五千年黎中國偉大文化 一定要入引中國醫生解決香港班仆街醫生<br />\n好撚唔抵得佢地咁高人工，一定要拉到佢1萬5千蚊一個月 低過洗碗阿姐！！！！！！ 大家一齊跟我大字報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孕婦剖腹產子被偷腎 中國新華醫院院長供認曾偷九個腎<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=3b387d0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&h=24a56f2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608</a><br />\n<br />\n手術後腎消失 農婦尋腎3年無果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2015%2F01%2F29%2Fa1172952.html&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=6911b37c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html</a><br />\n<br />\n包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！ 病人負傷起來繳費<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=41f8de33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&h=c41842b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費</a><br />\n<br />\n重慶醫生手術途中突加碼　費用飆升13倍<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151130%2Fbkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=4894f1fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇男割包皮　醫生手術中加價5倍　院方：沒違規 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181205/s00004/1543977455217/江蘇男割包皮-醫生手術中加價5倍-院方-沒違規\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181205%2Fs00004%2F1543977455217%2F%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E7%94%B7%E5%89%B2%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B95%E5%80%8D-%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B9-%E6%B2%92%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=d65e050d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181205%2Fs00004%2F1543977455217%2F%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E7%94%B7%E5%89%B2%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B95%E5%80%8D-%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B9-%E6%B2%92%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F&h=3aa50e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181205/s00004/1543977455217/江蘇男割包皮-醫生手術中加價5倍-院方-沒違規</a><br />\n<br />\n成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦　警方：嫌犯現已被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/191422/成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦-警方-嫌犯現已被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F191422%2F%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89%E5%BE%8C%E7%AB%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%AB%8C%E7%8A%AF%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=befcedad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/191422/成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦-警方-嫌犯現已被捕</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/288428/成都無牌醫生將女患者麻醉後強姦-多項罪成獲刑6年4個月\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%2F288428%2F%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E7%89%8C%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%87%E5%A5%B3%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89%E5%BE%8C%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%A4%9A%E9%A0%85%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%916%E5%B9%B44%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=d0814d83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/288428/成都無牌醫生將女患者麻醉後強姦-多項罪成獲刑6年4個月</a><br />\n<br />\n辦案人員經查發現，羅平沒有取得醫師資格證和醫師執業證。他於2017年6月開始在雙流區某街道開設的「1+1服務中心」從事醫療活動，並辦理虛假的醫師資格證、醫師執業證和身份證，向雙流區某醫院提交。他又於2016年至2018年期間，階段性在雙流某醫院坐診。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">強姦，偷腎，加價 少不免 沒事兒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議香港政府先提出引入英國醫生 然後再偷偷地引入大陸醫生<br />\n咁樣就可以拉低醫生人工，我最想見到既事情先會發生！！！<br />\n我要佢地死！！！！！！！！！</span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n自2012年起，醫管局以有限度註冊聘請了39名海外醫生來港執業，但截至2018年底只有10名仍在公立醫院服務，「事實是醫管局無法挽留本港的畢業醫生，也無法挽留海外畢業的醫生。」<br />\n<br />\n林晢玄早前接受訪問時指，可參考新加坡模式，讓指定院校名單的海外醫生免試到本港公立醫院工作，年期不限。有關建議可謂是「改良版」的有限度註冊制度。<br />\n<br />\n而公共醫療醫生協會今日（30日）再發表聲明，指歡迎任何擁有與本港同等專業資格的海外畢業醫生，遵從現有機制，且透過有限度註冊來港，但需確保海外醫生長期留在公立醫院。<br />\n<br />\n香港公共醫療醫生協會稱，政府在2003年沙士削減2667張病床、推俗稱「肥雞餐」的自願離職計劃、關閉護士學校、削減醫科學額，緊縮醫療開資，而這些措施的惡果終在十多年後出現。協會指香港公營醫療體系早就超出負荷，而醫院的工作環境已達不安全水平，嚴重危害病人安全及影響服務質素，而前線醫護仍一直努力工作，「哀我同業，咫尺但愁雷雨至，向來悲傷何其多？」<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以香港戰地環境引入高質英國醫生！<br />\n可能外國鬼佬鍾意戰地環境同埋語言挑戰</span></strong></span><br />\n大中華呢3個字已經夠吸引佢地<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢地NHS d醫院 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJYOBJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJYOBJo.jpg&h=b6235a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrxvP3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrxvP3q.jpg&h=62b8bafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4knr7P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4knr7P6.jpg&h=d20ccc63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b60UxgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb60UxgO.jpg&h=af70738c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYP95BR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYP95BR.jpg&h=2b03b738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我地香港d醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQWHGas.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQWHGas.jpg&h=eb01e00e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyJGcg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyJGcg9.jpg&h=a2c8d832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xsLDXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xsLDXa.jpg&h=ca2fec23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skczxhm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkczxhm.jpg&h=ed64d856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tjeexhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeexhq.jpg&h=ac181a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">英聯邦高質醫生一定好鍾意挑戰自己 快d邀請佢地黎香港做野</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"30d475f0c945a91b8045d06b06f95807a68a0e44","tid":1005725,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"017a9b84cd2b301e38ffe43536374507b540ea46","tid":1005725,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:12:47.000Z","msg":"push"}]}